/a>)、緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>3. 投信當日 (22) 賣超的股票<br/>元大台灣50 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0050:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0050\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0050-TW</a>)、兆豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2886:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2886\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2886-TW</a>)、緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)、光寶科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2301-TW</a>)<br/> </p></section></main>",
